en:
The [b]Time Sampling Form[/b] is a guided observation tool. You set the length of your observation in minutes. Every 20 seconds, you click the button that corresponds with the behaviour you observe at that time. 

The buttons to select the observed behaviour will be visible in the final 5 seconds of each 20 second interval. 

For first time users: It is recommended to do a one-minute trial to gain familiarity with the system. I hope you find this tool useful!
You must complete all fields below!
How long will you observe for? (in minutes)
